### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5229

### List all todos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/todo

### Create a new todo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/todo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Pass the interview",
  "description": "Build backend and frontend"
}

### Update the todo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/todo/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Build backend, frontend and infrastructure"
}

### Toggle completion status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/todo/1/toggle

### Get a todo by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/todo/1

### Delete a todo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/todo/1

